{"tid":2501153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務院：蔡玉玲奪得「金堯如新聞自由獎」肯定了她對新聞自由的重要貢獻","createTime":"2021-04-23T07:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:44:56.000Z","uid":227801,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a93bcef1e9d9422d98e4aaebe8ad8bf2f8fb4754","tid":2501153,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"美國國務院對蔡玉玲判刑感失望　指蔡玉玲只是做好工作<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人普賴斯對香港電台節目《鏗鏘集－7.21誰主真相》編導蔡玉玲的判刑表示極度失望，認為蔡玉玲只是做好自己的工作，她最近奪得「金堯如新聞自由獎」，獎項肯定她對新聞自由的重要貢獻，而新聞自由是受《中英聯合聲明》保障。蔡玉玲因跟進採訪元朗7.21事件，就車牌資料查冊，其後被警方拘捕，西九龍裁判法院昨日裁定她兩項作出虛假陳述罪成，共罰款6000元。<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-23 15:03:25"},{"pid":"1aadc02c51ac762ccb8f8b3ba38deb71762499b1","tid":2501153,"uid":47775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"美國國務院都出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6317b92b853496ee853726ec3cac672b47c7e18","tid":2501153,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ede47cbcf0e29238e09508d3fe42b353f1775c","tid":2501153,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6cded22851072aeead1d8b2a9226fa60d0030b","tid":2501153,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aadc02c51ac762ccb8f8b3ba38deb71762499b1","tid":2501153,"uid":47775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"美國國務院都出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"港共班柒頭成日助攻打國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"